const faqs = [
  {
    q: "Who owns Groen?",
    a: "Groen is part of Ali Group, the Italian privately-held foodservice equipment holding company. Ali Group acquired Groen around 2001. Sister brands within Ali Group include Beverage-Air (commercial refrigeration), Scotsman (ice machines), Ice-O-Matic (ice machines), Champion (commercial dishwashers), Cleveland Range (steam equipment, also Ali Group at the corporate parent level via Welbilt acquisition), and ~25 other foodservice brands. The corporate structure means Ali Group's parts and service network is well-developed and OEM parts availability is strong across the Groen product family.",
