<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">Groen · Ali Group Portfolio · Illinois Since 1947 · LA Same-Day</p>
    <h1>Groen Steam Kettle Repair Los Angeles</h1>
    <p class="lede">Groen steam jacketed kettle service across LA, Orange, Ventura, San Bernardino, Riverside. TDB gas-fired tilt kettles, AH-1E electric tilt kettles, INA direct-steam, ABC braising pans. Ali Group portfolio since ~2001. $120 commercial diagnostic, waived with repair. BHGS #A49573, EPA 608 Universal certified #1346255700410.</p>
